{"aid": "izpowt6i1wl4n0", "result": {"status": "active", "unique_views": 23, "request_instructor_me": false, "change_log": [{"type": "create", "anon": "no", "when": "2017-02-28T01:49:36Z", "data": "izovl421hm36wd", "uid": "ie7xy5sipx51qz"}], "upvote_ids": [], "id": "izovl40ssrw6wb", "bookmarked": 4, "tags": ["lecture3", "student"], "i_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "children": [], "nr": 992, "bucket_order": 2, "type": "note", "folders": ["lecture3"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 0, "bucket_name": "Today", "q_edits": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor": 0, "created": "2017-02-28T01:49:36Z", "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "s_edits": [], "my_favorite": false, "default_anonymity": "no", "t": 1488295831482, "tag_good": [{"name": "Yu Chen", "admin": true, "photo": "1378950179_35.png", "us": false, "id": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "所有老师和助教_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "email": "yuchen@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn", "admin_permission": 10}], "tag_good_arr": ["hcrrjuyequh4bt"], "history": [{"content": "<p>向勇老师在MOOC第3.4节8:06左右时提到&#xff1a;</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“最后我们还有一个问题需要来讨论&#xff0c;就是我在什么时候用系统调用&#xff0c;什么时候用函数调用。”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>一开始我对这句话不是很理解。一些功能&#xff08;如文件读写&#xff09;由内核态完成&#xff0c;我们只能用系统调用实现&#xff0c;只用函数调用不能实现。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>但实际上这个问题针对的是操作系统设计者&#xff0c;而不是操作系统使用者。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>在软件工程的实践中&#xff0c;某些功能是放在用户态还是内核态实现是由OS开发者选择的。放在内核态能有更高的效率&#xff0c;但如果功能实现有漏洞&#xff0c;在内核态会造成更大的安全隐患&#xff0c;适合放在内核态。在某些Linux版本中&#xff0c;GUI被放在内核态实现&#xff0c;有些则在用户态实现。对于我们这种OS设计者&#xff0c;我们应该对功能分配做出最好的判断。</p>", "anon": "no", "created": "2017-02-28T01:49:36Z", "uid": "ie7xy5sipx51qz", "subject": "函数调用和系统调用的“选择”问题"}]}, "error": null}